description._content: Description: Government House. Seychelles. Built under direction of His Excellency Governor W.E. Davidson, C.M.G. Commenced 1911. - Completed 1913. Location: Seychelles Date: 1911 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/771 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
